🔷 🔥 Flow
URL → /edit/5 → @PathVariable → id=5 → Controller
🔥 PathVariable vs QueryParam
Feature	PathVariable	RequestParam
URL	/book/101	/book?id=101
Usage	Resource ID	Filters/search
Annotation	@PathVariable	@RequestParam
